data.description: Beautiful & well maintained home in a highly desirable neighborhood! Enjoy having two large living-rooms, one with a fireplace, large formal dining area, & a spacious eat-in kitchen w/ breakfast nook and all stainless steel appliances! This home has been updated w/ new paint & floors, & a luxurious remodeled master bath! Huge walk in shower, double vanities, & a one of a kind tile design! The master bedroom has a huge walk in closet w/ tons of storage and washer & dryer hook ups are located in the master closet for easy access! Large backyard, 2 car attached garage, & more to see! Call today to set up your private tour!
